name: Dark Matter: Output 300421b - 3750x3750 PNG
description: One of a series of outputs from a generative particle system created in Processing by @mikebrondbjerg. | Ideologies, political forces and digital technologies often go unseen, but exert an enormous force on, and shape our society. These forces are often only made visible and revealed by the change in our collective behaviour around them. Dark Matter is an ongoing series of generative images and motion graphics that attempt to visualise this.
